#### Dynamic Results — Applied to IriScale

**The Big Reveal:**

Visual speedometer or progress bar showing "AI Content Marketing Readiness Score" out of 100%.

| Score Range | Dynamic Message |
|-------------|-----------------|
| **80-100%** | "Congratulations — you've got strong foundations. You're ready to supercharge your content marketing with AI automation." |
| **50-79%** | "You've got solid foundations, but there's significant room to improve. A few key changes could dramatically increase your results." |
| **0-49%** | "There's a lot of opportunity ahead. Most businesses in your position see rapid improvement once they put the right systems in place." |

**Three Personalized Insights (change based on their weakest areas):**

| Weak Area | Insight |
|-----------|---------|
| AI Search Visibility (Q3, Q6 scored low) | "You're invisible to AI search. When your customers ask ChatGPT or Perplexity about your industry, your competitors are showing up — not you. IriScale tracks your visibility across 5 AI platforms and helps you create optimized answers that get cited." |
| Content Strategy (Q1, Q2, Q5, Q7 scored low) | "Without a centralized knowledge base and structured content plan, you're creating content in the dark. IriScale's Content Architect AI generates a complete website hierarchy from your business data in minutes." |
| Social & Opportunity Capture (Q8, Q10 scored low) | "Right now, your potential customers are discussing their problems on Reddit and social media — and you're not in the conversation. IriScale's Opportunity Agent monitors these platforms and gives you AI-generated responses to engage with." |

**Next Steps (tiered by qualifying answers):**

| Qualification | Trigger (from Part C answers) | Next Step |
|--------------|-------------------------------|-----------|
| **Hot lead** | Maturity = plateauing or mature + Solution = software or managed service + Clear desired outcome | "Book a personalized demo — we'll show you IriScale configured for your specific industry" → Route to sales |
| **Warm lead** | Maturity = ad hoc or growing + Solution = guided onboarding or not sure | "Watch a 5-minute platform walkthrough" + enter email nurture sequence showing relevant features based on their weak areas |
| **Cool lead** | Maturity = just starting + Solution = training first or not sure + Obstacle = budget | "Download our free AI Content Marketing Playbook" + monthly educational newsletter |

**Bottom of page:** IriScale website link, social media profiles, contact email — let people explore further.

