## Part 3: Implementation Plan

### Tool Decision: How to Build the Assessment

| Option | Pros | Cons | Recommendation |
|--------|------|------|----------------|
| **ScoreApp** | Quick setup (10-30 min per Priestley), 150 templates, proven system, built-in dashboard, dynamic results logic included | Monthly cost, external dependency, limited branding, another tool to manage, data lives outside IriScale | **Start here for speed** |
| **Typeform / Tally + custom scoring** | Better branding control, cheaper, own the data | Manual scoring logic, no built-in dashboard, more setup | Good alternative if ScoreApp too expensive |
| **Build into IriScale** | Ultimate dog-fooding, could become customer feature, full data ownership, auto-ingest website URL into Knowledge Base | Development time, not core focus | **Long-term vision** — build once validated |

> **Recommended approach:** Launch with ScoreApp to validate the concept fast. Once you have conversion data and proven question set, evaluate building it into IriScale as a lead gen feature that IriScale customers could also use for their own businesses.

### Lead Nurture Integration

| Lead Tier | Email Sequence | Content |
|-----------|---------------|---------|
| **Hot** | Immediate booking confirmation + sales prep | Demo booking link, case studies, "what to expect" email |
| **Warm** | 5-7 email drip over 2 weeks | Email 1: Platform walkthrough video. Emails 2-5: One feature deep-dive per email matched to their weak areas. Email 6: Case study. Email 7: Demo offer |
| **Cool** | Monthly newsletter + quarterly re-assessment | Educational content, industry insights, quarterly "retake the assessment" CTA to re-engage |

### Metrics to Track

| Metric | Priestley's Benchmark | Our Target |
|--------|----------------------|------------|
| Landing page → quiz start rate | **20-40%** | TBD |
| Quiz completion rate | Not stated | TBD |
| Lead → demo booking rate | Not stated | TBD |
| Demo → customer conversion rate | N/A | TBD |
| Cost per lead (paid) | Not stated | TBD |
| Organic traffic to assessment | N/A | TBD |

